The evidence with the title 'Fact-checking claims about the individual mandate | politifact ' says Jun 28, 2012  ... Another bit of irony : Some Republicans had supported a plan with a mandate in the early 1990s as an alternative to a health care plan proposed by then president Bill Clinton. Liberal commentators pointed out that sen. Orrin Hatch Co-sponsored a 1993 health care bill that had an individual mandate. 
